<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="google-site-verification" content="ABJP0tmcFFoBAAvs9LJqvDWqY358NyoEZCn3msywQZc" />
    <title>WhatsCalendar - Sincronização Inteligente</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #00E676;
            --primary-dark: #00C853;
            --accent: #2979FF;
            --bg: #F4F7FE;
            --text-dark: #2B3674;
            --text-gray: #A3AED0;
            --card-bg: #FFFFFF;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            background: var(--bg);
            background-image: linear-gradient(135deg, #F4F7FE 0%, #E2EDF8 100%);
            color: var(--text-dark);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .main-content {
            flex-grow: 1;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 20px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        .container {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            padding: 40px 30px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(112, 144, 176, 0.12);
            max-width: 400px;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        /* Subtle Top Gradient Line */
        .container::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 5px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent), var(--primary));
        }

        .logo-box {
            width: 250px;
            height: 250px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            margin: 0 auto 20px auto;
        }
        
        .logo-box img {
            max-width: 100%;
            max-height: 100%;
            object-fit: contain;
            /* drop-shadow ensures any transparency looks great */
            filter: drop-shadow(0 8px 16px rgba(0, 230, 118, 0.2)); 
        }

        h1 { 
            font-weight: 700; 
            font-size: 24px; 
            margin-bottom: 12px; 
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }

        p { 
            color: var(--text-gray); 
            font-size: 14px; 
            margin-bottom: 30px; 
            line-height: 1.6; 
            font-weight: 400;
        }

        form {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 15px;
        }

        input[type="text"], input[type="time"] {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 16px;
            background: #F4F7FE;
            border: 1px solid transparent;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-size: 15px;
            color: var(--text-dark);
            box-sizing: border-box;
            outline: none;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }

        input[type="text"]:focus, input[type="time"]:focus {
            background: #FFFFFF;
            border-color: var(--primary);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(0, 230, 118, 0.15);
        }

        button {
            width: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary) 0%, var(--primary-dark) 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 16px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 200, 83, 0.2);
        }

        button:hover { 
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 20px rgba(0, 200, 83, 0.3);
        }

        button:active {
            transform: translateY(0);
        }

        /* Footer Google Auth Requirement */
        .footer-links {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: transparent;
        }

        .footer-links a {
            color: var(--text-gray);
            font-size: 13px;
            text-decoration: underline;
            margin: 0 10px;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: color 0.2s ease;
        }

        .footer-links a:hover {
            color: var(--text-dark);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="main-content">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="logo-box">
                <img src="/logo/logo_sf.png" alt="WhatsCalendar Logo">
            </div>
            <h1>WhatsCalendar</h1>
            <p>Conecte sua agenda e receba as notificações dos seus compromissos no WhatsApp todas as manhãs.</p>
            <form action="/connect" method="POST">
                <input type="text" id="whatsappInput" name="whatsappNumber" placeholder="55 (11) 99999-9999" required maxlength="19">
                <label style="text-align: left; font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-gray); margin-bottom: -10px; font-weight: 500;">Qual horário (Brasília) você deseja receber a agenda?</label>
                <input type="time" name="preferredTime" value="07:00" required>
                <button type="submit">Conectar Google Agenda</button>
            </form>
            <div style="margin-top: 25px; text-align: center; display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 20px;">
                <a href="https://whatscalendar-1.onrender.com/privacidade" style="color: #A3AED0; font-size: 13px; text-decoration: underline;">Privacy Policy</a>
                <a href="/admin" style="color: #A3AED0; font-size: 13px; text-decoration: underline;">Acesso Admin</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script>
        const whatsappInput = document.getElementById('whatsappInput');
        whatsappInput.addEventListener('input', function(e) {
            let x = e.target.value.replace(/\D/g, '');
            if (x.length > 0) {
                if (x.length <= 2) {
                    x = x; 
                } else if (x.length <= 4) {
                    x = x.replace(/^(\d{2})(\d+)/, "$1 ($2");
                } else if (x.length <= 9) {
                    x = x.replace(/^(\d{2})(\d{2})(\d+)/, "$1 ($2) $3");
                } else {
                    x = x.replace(/^(\d{2})(\d{2})(\d{5})(\d{0,4}).*/, "$1 ($2) $3-$4");
                }
            }
            e.target.value = x;
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
